:

1. *On* je bio zadovoljan rezultatima. (He was satisfied with the results.)
2. Ona je bila zadovoljna činjenicom da je uspela. (She was satisfied with the fact that she succeeded.)
3. Njegova zadovoljstvo je bilo vidljivo. (His satisfaction was visible.)
4. *Zadovoljstvo* je bilo izraženo na licu. (Satisfaction was expressed on the face.)
5. Oni su bili zadovoljni promenom. (They were pleased with the change.)